```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Identité"
        P[Python Scout] -->|SHA-256| D(discovered)
    end
    subgraph "Analyse & Vérité"
        D --> A(analyzed)
        A -->|Truth Binding| C(contracted)
    end
    subgraph "Synthèse & Patching"
        C --> PL(planned)
        PL -->|AST Engine| PT(patched)
    end
    subgraph "Certification"
        PT --> V(validated)
        V -->|Done| F[Clone RGL V2]
    end
```

